Class TavolettaSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.search.adversarial.IterativeDeepeningAlphaBetaSearch<State,Action,State.Turn>
      • it.unibo.ai.didattica.competition.tablut.gionnino9000.search.TavolettaSearch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    aima.core.search.adversarial.AdversarialSearch<State,Action>

    public class TavolettaSearch
extends aima.core.search.adversarial.IterativeDeepeningAlphaBetaSearch<State,Action,State.Turn>
    "Custom" implementation of AIMA Iterative Deepening MinMax search with Alpha-Beta Pruning. Maximal computation time is specified in seconds. This configuration redefines the method eval() using getUtility() method in GameAshtonTablut.
    See Also:
    IterativeDeepeningAlphaBetaSearch
